=== Purchase Information === Product Title: 3D Mink Eyelashes Natural Long Lashes 2 in 1 Self-adhesive Eyeliner Instead of Adhesive 5 Different Styles Pairs Kits Sets with Tweezers , NO NEED GLUE Review Date: 2020/08/27 Store: PURELEOR Average Rating: 3.9 Product Details: {'Brand': 'PURELEOR', 'Material': 'Mink Fur', 'Item Form': 'Pair', 'Mounting Type': 'Eyelash Glue', 'Unit Count': '5.00 Count', 'Package Dimensions': '9 x 6 x 1 inches; 2.4 Ounces', 'UPC': '750810450143'} Review Text: Pros: it came with everything pictured, a lash applicator, the tube of “eyeliner glue” and 5 pairs of lashes in varying thickness. The box itself was nicely packaged. For reference, I used the thinnest/most natural pair at the top for my review.

Cons: the tube of eyeliner was either sitting so long it completely dried up, or the glue caused the eyeliner to adhere to the inside of the tube, but it was almost impossible to get ANY of the liner on my lid.

When I finally got a line to go on, it was akin to what attempting to using a dried up Expo on whiteboard looks like- I had to scrub the pen on my eyelid in an attempt to lay down any product at all, resulting in a very pitiful looking eyeliner application.

I fixed the lashes to the appropriate area, and within 5 minutes they were coming off at the corners. I tried to remedy the overall result somewhat by adding my own liner, and that example is on the second photo, bottom right corner (photo with eyeshadow applied).

The lashes themselves were the quality you’d expect from a multi pack at this price. Some of the individual lashes had fallen out as I opened the package as well.

Final thoughts: just use eyelash glue and get quality lashes. It doesn’t take any more time to apply and at least you can apply eyeliner to suit your taste. Review Title: Glue + Eyeliner probably shouldn’t mix Rating: 2.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: 7JHH WIGS Long Wavy Curly Wig With Bangs Natural Hair Dye Wig for Women (25inch, Red) Review Date: 2021/08/13 Store: 7JHH WIGS Average Rating: 4.7 Product Details: {'Item Dimensions LxWxH': '13.78 x 8.66 x 1.57 inches', 'Hair Type': 'Wavy, Curly', 'Brand': '7JHH WIGS', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Product Dimensions': '13.78 x 8.66 x 1.57 inches; 12.7 Ounces', 'UPC': '682601933330'} Review Text: This wig is nice but a little thin, the value for money is great though. The bangs especially are really cute if you get them positioned correctly. Review Title: Nice wig, a little thin Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: OULAC Shine to Shine Velvet Matte Lipstick, Long Lasting Creamy Formula, Opaque Finish, Vegan Friendly, 3.6 grams / 0.12 ounces, Cranberries (Y09) Review Date: 2021/11/05 Store: Oulac Average Rating: 3.7 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Oulac', 'Item Form': 'Cream', 'Finish Type': 'Matte,Velvet', 'Product Benefits': 'Long Lasting,Shine', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Product Dimensions': '3.9 x 0.68 x 0.68 inches; 1.23 Ounces', 'Item model number': 'velvet-matte-Y09'} Review Text: This lipstick is gorgeous! Applies very easily and comes in a steel lipstick container that seems very durable. Super cute packaging and the product goes on without issue. It does smudge some but as it’s not a matte product that’s to be expected, it’s also not drying and feels great on the lips for all day wear. Review Title: Beautiful, vibrant colors with nice smell Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: OULAC Blush Mono 4.8g/0.16oz (One More time) Review Date: 2021/11/05 Store: OUL'AC Product Description: ['Smooth Glide', ': A silky, superfine blush delivers a burst of buildable colors that are designed for every skin tone. Vitamin E acts as an essential emollient with antioxidant properties to restore flexibility, prevent dryness and color-fading.', 'Natural Finish', ': The richly-pigmented, long-lasting formula glides seamlessly on the skin and easily blends for an irresistibly radiant, healthy-looking complexion.', 'Intense Payoff', ': Mineral pigments allow for high color payoff and smooth application, while micronized powder ensures excellent blendability and a true matte finish. Vegan Friendly!'] Average Rating: 4.6 Product Details: {'Item Form': 'Powder', 'Finish Type': 'Matte', 'Coverage': 'Buildable', 'Brand': "OUL'AC", 'Skin Tone': 'All'} Review Text: This blush is beautiful! It’s a soft pink color that goes on easily and is smooth and creamy when applying. It’s easy to build the color up to the desired effect and stays on without fading for hours. Review Title: Absolutely gorgeous blush, buildable color Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: AISI QUEENS Black Wigs for Women Long Wavy Curly Synthetic Lace Front Wig Middle Part Body Wavy Hair Replacement Wigs Heat Resistant Fibers for Daily Party Use Review Date: 2021/11/05 Store: AISI QUEENS Average Rating: 4.0 Product Details: {'Material': 'Synthetic', 'Hair Type': 'Wavy', 'Brand': 'AISI QUEENS', 'Package Dimensions': '10.75 x 9.09 x 2.72 inches; 11.36 Ounces'} Review Text: I love this lace front wig, it came with wig caps and was easy to trim the lace where I needed it. This would be a great wig for daily wear or cosplay, if you’re doing daily wear I’d suggest thinning it a little unless you like the fuller appearance. On me it looks like too much volume so i used thinning scissors and corrected that and then was able to apply the wig and wear it without issue! It looks great and realistic. Review Title: Cute wig for a great price, easy to wear Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Eyebrow Stamp Stencil Kit 2 Colors Waterproof and Long Lasting One Step Easy Color Brow Stamp with 24 Eyebrow Stencils, 1 Brush and 1 Razor, Dark Brown and Light Brown Review Date: 2021/11/26 Store: Marine Forest Average Rating: 3.2 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Marine Forest', 'Item Form': 'Powder', 'Finish Type': 'Natural', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Product Benefits': 'Long Lasting', 'Product Dimensions': '4.65 x 0.67 x 0.67 inches; 2.4 Ounces', 'Item model number': 'ES7010-2brown', 'UPC': '762403888318'} Review Text: It works fine and the stencils are made well, but the powders themselves are weirdly colored- one is too dark and the other is almost orange. If you have really dark hair one side of the powder may work well for you but it applies almost like a marker (I did pat it on as you’re supposed to), and I prefer a more natural look. Review Title: Okay but powders are too dark Rating: 3.0 --------------------------------------------------

SUMMARY:  
The individual demonstrates a preference for beauty products that emphasize quality and ease of application, as indicated by consistently high ratings for wigs and makeup items. They notably favor products that are long-lasting, user-friendly, and well-packaged, reflecting an appreciation for aesthetic appeal and functionality. 

Themes suggest a strong inclination towards products that enhance appearance with minimal hassle, such as self-adhesive beauty items. However, they also exhibit a degree of price sensitivity, preferring items that offer good value for money, particularly in the wig category. Although they have a varied taste in shades and finishes, there are concerns regarding product efficacy and component quality, especially when it comes to attachments and adhesives. 

Quality matters significantly; the individual expresses disappointment with products that fared poorly in function, like the eyeliner's failure to adhere properly, contrasting with high satisfaction for well-performing items. In sum, their core preference leans towards vegan-friendly, effective cosmetics, and user-friendly hair treatments at a reasonable price without compromising on quality.

target_interaction.title: Great for tired eyes!
target_interaction.text: I absolutely love these. I’ve been using them for a week now and they feel so nice on my skin. they’re very gentle so they’d be great for those with sensitive skin. They’re easy to apply and come in a cute jar to keep the rest sealed. They’re great to use at night before bed to freshen your under eyes.
